values:
I am still with Marius and I am feeling much better as of late. I know I rant and rave alot. I want you all to know that it is mainly my own childish insecurities I am voicing here. I never really think anyone is going to answer me back. I get used to talking to myself. *small smile* I have seen so many quized circulating so I thought I would do a few and pass them around. It looks like it's going to start raining here soon enough. Another drizzly night is in store for tonight. I wonder if Marius would accompany me tonight and perhaps catch some dinner with me? I do love knowing he's with me while we dine. I love the way he tries not to watch. So polite of him. I know he wants to watch secretly. It for some reason fascinates him. I will admit I am a bit of an exhibitionist at times but mainly when I know he's watching.
You will go to jail for:
Peeing in public



Take this quiz at QuizGalaxy.com
Hmm...I suppose with my aforementioned confession this should come as no surprise. *lol*
Your darkest secret is:
You once told someone to bring it



Take this quiz at QuizGalaxy.com
*lmao* I believe it was, Lestat I said that to once. Wasn't it?

It has been a while since I last updated. I have been silenced because of all that has happened around us. Like anyone else when life seems to get too heavy I seek refuge. I have been with Marius now for a few weeks. Still I feel strange. Some what alone. This feeling is hard to describe. I know what he explained to me before my coming here and I fully respect what he has to do, but I still wish it could be different for us from time to time. I despise this woman who has taken up so much of his precious time. I could take her life myself and be done with her and her family. Yet I don't, I stay silent and in the back drop just waiting on Marius' every word or sign of affection.

I wonder if he feels what I feel. I wonder if he at times takes the liberty to try and read my desires? How many nights I have wandered alone only to find myself watching him like a stalker. I feel so utterly ridiculous sometimes I make my self nausious. Perhaps this wasn't such a good idea after all? I need to stop second guessing myself so much. No wonder the others still see me as a child, a young one. That last name irks me greatly and oddly enough it's one Marius is so fond of saying.

*Doing a little dance* 

I was just given a new layout by <Lj user=Lade_> I know it's blue but I like blue at the moment. It reminds me of Marius' eyes. They are gorgeous!! 

As I was saying...have a look and tell me what you think. Any comments are always welcomed.

Maharet: You're Obscure, You're Elusive, You're
down right scarey, but who cares, you have all
the knowledge and resources you could ever want
and that's all that matters! Who cares if
everyone thinks your a myth, right? It only
means you can work even harder on finding out
why we exsist!

brought to you by Quizilla Hmm...that was pretty accurate. I wonder if I am even a possible answer in this quiz? Probably not. Oh well.

Who Were You In a Past Life?
Your Daddy Is Arnold Schwarzenegger
What You Call Him: Big Daddy Why You Love Him: He's your sugar daddy
Who's Your Daddy?
Yes, I know I am doing a ton of these. I am nervous. I have been thrown a curve ball. I am not sure to accept it or throw it back? She saw me. She actually spoke to me. I was speechless. I have hunted her for days maybe even weeks now. They all run together I have lost all track of time on my quest for her. I don't know what to do now. Stop? Let go? Move on? Kill her? Don't? I am indecisive when I have been caught unawares and now I am afraid the sad reality has set in. Beautiful as she is, she must die for I must have her. *moistening lips in anticipation*

Emo Kid
You are 14% Rational, 28% Extroverted, 42% Brutal, and 28% Arrogant.
You are the Emo Kid, best described as a quiet pussy! You tend to be an intuitive rather than a logical thinker, meaning you rely more on your feelings than your thoughts. Not only that, but you are introverted, gentle, and rather humble. You embody all the traits of the perfect emo kid. You are a push-over, an emotional thinker, gentle to the extent of absurdity, and so humble that it even makes Jesus puke. If you write poetry, you no doubt write angsty, syrupy lines about depression, sadness, and other such redundant states of emo-being. Your personality is defective because you are too gentle, rather underconfident in yourself, decidely lacking in any rational thought, and also a bit too inhibited.

I probably made you cry, didn't I? Fucking Emo Kid.

To put it less negatively:

1. You are more INTUITIVE than rational.

2. You are more INTROVERTED than extroverted.

3. You are more GENTLE than brutal.

4. You are more HUMBLE than arrogant.

Compatibility:

Your exact opposite is the Smartass.

Other personalities you would probably get along with are the Hippie, the Televangelist, and the Starving Artist.

*

*

If you scored near fifty percent for a certain trait (42%-58%), you could very well go either way. For example, someone with 42% Extroversion is slightly leaning towards being an introvert, but is close enough to being an extrovert to be classified that way as well. Below is a list of the other personality types so that you can determine which other possible categories you may fill if you scored near fifty percent for certain traits.

The other personality types:

The Emo Kid: Intuitive, Introverted, Gentle, Humble.

The Starving Artist: Intuitive, Introverted, Gentle, Arrogant.

The Bitch-Slap: Intuitive, Introverted, Brutal, Humble.

The Brute: Intuitive, Introverted, Brutal, Arrogant.

The Hippie: Intuitive, Extroverted, Gentle, Humble.

The Televangelist: Intuitive, Extroverted, Gentle, Arrogant.

The Schoolyard Bully: Intuitive, Extroverted, Brutal, Humble.

The Class Clown: Intuitive, Extroverted, Brutal, Arrogant.

The Robot: Rational, Introverted, Gentle, Humble.

The Haughty Intellectual: Rational, Introverted, Gentle, Arrogant.

The Spiteful Loner: Rational, Introverted, Brutal, Humble.

The Sociopath: Rational, Introverted, Brutal, Arrogant.

The Hand-Raiser: Rational, Extroverted, Gentle, Humble.

The Braggart: Rational, Extroverted, Gentle, Arrogant.

The Capitalist Pig: Rational, Extroverted, Brutal, Humble.

The Smartass: Rational, Extroverted, Brutal, Arrogant.




My test tracked 4 variables How you compared to other people your age and gender:
You scored higher than 10% on Rationality
 You scored higher than 20% on Extroversion
 You scored higher than 45% on Brutality
 You scored higher than 20% on Arrogance
Link: The Personality Defect Test written by saint_gasoline on Ok Cupid

I am sitting here at my desk surrounded by stacks and stacks of files and books. I know I have mountains of things to keep my busy but I don't want to be busy. I want to do nothing or useless things that have no significance whatsoever. I should just skip out shouldn't I? *light laugh* I never skipped school or an appointment a day in my mortal life. I was such a "good" kid it was sickening. 

I feel like going for a ride aboard a ship. I think I will. A small mini-trip nothing extravagant just something to help myself unwind. I wonder if I could persuade my Aunt or even Khayman to come along for a night or two? Hmm.

Stefan, I know you mentioned that if you missed one day not posting that perhaps we should wonder why? I am wondering right now and I hope that nothing has befallen you my poet of the night. Come back on here soon for you presence is missed.
